<span class="score" id="comment_score_2085120">(<a href="reversethis-%7Bmoc.liamg%7D%7Bta%7D%7B70041kxr%7D" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 2085120); return false">スコア:2</a>, 興味深い)</span></h4>
